reviews.text: Good service and decent seating for a mall coffee shop.
The seats are beautiful and comfortable.
A nice Pacific Coffee branch with an acceptably large and comfy seating area. Friendly and forthcoming staff.

Comfortable environment. Free wifi. Delicious coffee with the choices of milk, skimmed milk and soy milk.   Sandwiches with meat and vegetarian sandwiches. Nice and helpful staff. Iced chocolate, walnut maple coffee, fried chicken corn bread, curry vegetable pie.
Way Better than Starbutts.
